QuestData.Title: Lost in Action
QuestData.Description: You have to help me! We were sent here to investigate the various parts of the reservoir, but my friends haven't come back yet, and it's been a long time.$B$BThat's why I need you to discover what became of them. Naturalist Bite and Weeder Greenthumb went this way.
QuestData.LogDescription: Discover what happened to Naturalist Bite and Weeder Greenthumb. Then, return to Watcher Jhang.
QuestData.RewardText: The loss of life...it pains me.$B$B<Watcher Jhang sighs.>$B$BThank you, $n. When we are all reunited, the naga won't stand a chance.
